  "title": "Class 3 Driver (Boon Lay) - SS10",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Class 3 Driver</strong></li><li>Location: Boon Lay</li><li>6Days - 8AM - 5:00PM + OT (sometime only)</li><li>Basic $2300 - $2500 + AWS + Performance Bonus</li></ul><p><u><strong>Benefits:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Company vehicle provided (10ft. freezer truck, can request for vehicle drive home but subject to management approval) </li><li>Season parking & Diesel Provided</li><li>Medical and Leave Benefits</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Class 3 driving license</li></ul><p><u><strong>Job Scope</strong></u></p><ul><li>Safely and timely deliver frozen products to customers</li><li>Load and unload cargo</li><li>Able to carry up to 15kg ctns (if required)</li><li>Skill in using GPS</li><li>Follow traffic laws</li><li>Refuel and clean vehicle</li><li>Inspect trucks and record issues</li><li>Keep activities log and log hours</li></ul><p>Samuel Siaw</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd</p><p>EA No: 14C7279</p><p>Reg No: R2412474</p>",
